Salon Website UI/UX Design

Project Overview

This project focuses on designing a modern, responsive salon website UI that improves user experience and increases appointment bookings.

 🎯 Objective

To create a clean, conversion-focused interface that helps users:

Explore services easily
Build trust through testimonials
Book appointments seamlessly

Target Users

Young working professionals (20–35)
Individuals looking for premium salon services
Users who prefer quick and easy booking

Design Structure

 Homepage (Hero, Services, Reviews, Contact)
 Service Detail Page
 Contact / Lead Generation Form
 Mobile Responsive Layout

UX Decisions

 Clear CTA buttons for booking
 Minimal and clean layout for easy navigation
 Mobile-first approach for better usability
 Use of visual hierarchy for readability

Conversion Strategy

 WhatsApp CTA for instant booking
 Testimonials to build trust
 Simple form to reduce friction

Tools Used

 Figma
 Auto Layout
